    <item>
      <title>美联储鲍曼认为通胀存在上行风险，并暗示降息需谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/fed-s-bowman-sees-upside-inflation-risk-signals-caution-on-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事米歇尔鲍曼表示，她仍然认为通胀存在上行风险且劳动力市场持续走强，这表明她可能还没有准备好在 9 月份美国央行行长会议上支持降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/fed-s-bowman-sees-upside-inflation-risk-signals-caution-on-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 16:10:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
