      <title>美国盈利增长终于在科技巨头之外显现出来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/earnings-growth-is-finally-showing-up-outside-of-megacap-tech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国企业新一季度的财报季进入最后阶段，有一点是明确的：那些被排除在人工智能热潮之外的企业，期待已久的复苏终于开始了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/earnings-growth-is-finally-showing-up-outside-of-megacap-tech</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
